1. *Dobijaš* li platu ovog meseca? (Are you getting your salary this month?)
2. *Dobijaš* od mene 10 bodova za taj odgovor. (You get 10 points from me for that answer.)
3. Kada *dobijaš* poklon za rođendan? (When do you receive a birthday present?)
4. *Dobijaš* li redovno obaveštenja od kompanije? (Do you regularly receive updates from the company?)
5. Šta *dobijaš* kada se pridružiš našem programu vernosti? (What do you get when you join our loyalty program?)
6. *Dobijaš* priliku da putuješ svetom kada dobiješ stipendiju. (You get the opportunity to travel the world when you receive a scholarship.)
7. Ne *dobijaš* ono što želiš uvek. (You don't always get what you want.)
8. *Dobijaš* vreme za sebe kada odeš na odmor. (You get time for yourself when you go on vacation.)
9. On *dobija* kritike zbog svog lošeg ponašanja. (He receives criticism for his bad behavior.)
10. Kada *dobijemo* dozvolu za gradnju, moći ćemo da započnemo projekat. (When we receive the construction permit, we will be able to start the project.)